===Etymology===
:from Slavic root '''svet''' (''light''), i.e., the world that can be seen
===Noun===
:'''svet''' ''m'', '''svety''' ''pl''
:'''svet''' ''stem''
:'''sveta''' ''{{gensg}}''
:{{decpat}} {{dub}}
# the basic meaning is the [[world]]
# the [[cosmos]], the [[universe]], all there is
#:'''stvorenie sveta''' &ndash; ''the creation of the world''
# our own planet, the [[Earth]], the [[globe]]
#:'''cesta okolo sveta''' &ndash; ''journey around the world''
# foreign lands
#: '''ísť do sveta''' &ndash; ''literally, to go to the world, i.e., to go out exploring other places''
